This is the user facing part of the Loom project, for running mobile automation tests.
The sister project, Loom Controller (https://github.com/dchelstowski/loom-controller), should run on your tests machine, while Loom Web should be hosted somewhere that your users will be able to reach it.

If you don't already have mongodb, install it with:

'brew install mongodb'

Run mongodb with:

mongod --dbpath /path/to/project/data

Now start the server:

npm install

npm start

